items.name: Boneless Mutton
items.description: Low in fat with velvety pink and soft tender meat. Chosen from the best parts of the lamb especially from the hind of legs and cut in proportionate pieces by our butchers is perfect for making curries and kababs. With an array of cuts all you need is to decide how to cook.

items.name: Mutton Keema
items.description: Distinct flavorful succulent grounded meat minced specially by our butchers without any splinters or wastage. The lean trim meat is lamb lovers delight. Make melt in your mouth mutton balls mint chutney and make your meals a special.

items.name: Kidneys
items.description: Rich juicy flavourful and tender texture of the lamb kidneys are well liked by many. It has robust unique taste and is high in protein, iron and Vitamin A and B. It cooks fast and we deliver it fresh without any sinews and wastage. Whip up Gurda fry or masala and serve it hot with naan.

items.name: Mutton Boti
items.description: Mutton boti kabab or poriyal/ masala! All you need is just get the recipe ready and we will deliver it to you all cleaned and cut. Full of vitamins and essential nutrients, this is liked by many.

items.name: Legs
items.description: Succulent lamb trotters that adds an extreme flavour to soups and curry. It is nourishing delicacy that is a sure hit in your kitchen. Serve up the spicy hot paya curry with hot naan or rice.

items.name: Head Meat
items.description: This is a delicacy enjoyed by the few and we deliver it all cleaned and removed of all the wastage. Prepare your favourite soup or fry by just ordering from us. Our master butchers will take care that all the pre cleaning is done and so that all you need is to cook it.

items.name: Seena
items.description: Soft, juicy and succulent pieces from the chest. All expertly carved and cut by our master butchers to give you the best of cooking pleasure with all the goodness of lean and tender meat.

items.name: Chops
items.description: Selected from the ribs of the lamb and is carved specially by our butchers while being cleaned to the bone. Each chop is proportionately cut to 3 to 4 inches pieces and is perfect partner to your specials. Make your barbecues special by cooking our tender moist chops. Turn on the fire!!!

items.name: Liver
items.description: Increase your blood levels. Liver is a rich source of necessary iron and minerals and is low in fat and is high in protein. Pottel liver is shiny, firm and is cleaned of all sinews. Fry it up and taste the best.

items.name: Brain
items.description: Cook up this delicacy. Fresh and smooth in texture. It is high in protein and fat but has no carbs. This is an absolute meat lover's delight and is extremely tasty when cooked in Mughlai style bheja fry. Our chefs make sure you get the freshest and the best to keep the texture and taste

items.name: Rann / Thigh
items.description: Meat so tender and lean that this is the premium of our lamb range. Specially wanted by the meat lovers as it is a hit addition to that special meal. It has a very distinct taste and is moist to the bone.

items.name: Marrow Bones

items.description:
Make tangy, luscious, spicy and flavourful rasam or soup with the bones. It can be savoured by

good heart. Even our furry doggies go woof woof and wag their tail for this treat.

items.name: Tilli/Spleen
items.description: Tilli is taken from left side of the upper side of the abdomen. Dish up Bhuna tilli curry or fry cooked in desi ghee and add little goodness into your diet. Its shiny and firm and is generally liked by few mutton lovers.

items.name: Rohu
items.description: Rohu is a flavourful and moist fish that has defined bone structure. Cook up Rohu fry or maas charchadi with this fresh catch from the river!! Our chefs definitely recommend this to add the oomph to your blue plate. Available in various cuts just so that you could make a curry or a fry.

items.name: Catla/Botcha
items.description: Raise up the omegas and cook up Catla/JOHL. Fresh catch from the river to spice up your plate with a special distinct taste. It is a bony fish that is cut and cleaned to your choice. Firm and smooth texture of the fish makes it a cooking delight and is absolute value for your money.

items.name: Live Murrel/Korameenu
items.description: Say hello to our local river fish and order a LIVE one. It is our king of delicacies and is sure to heat up a storm in your kitchen. It is perfect for fillets, grills, curries and fries. Cook it any style and stock up on lean protein, fat and omega 3.

items.name: Vanjaram/Seer Fish
items.description: Make way for the king of the ocean. He is loaded with all the best you need: unique taste, flavour and all the good protein and essential omegas. It can be grilled or made into succulent mouth watering Biryani. You just can’t go wrong with it. Perfect for children to as it has just one central bone and is cut into perfect steaks by our master butchers.

items.name: Bangada/Indian Mackerel
items.description: It is Bangada time! Fresh catch from the sea. Grill or fry us whole and we sure will fill up your kitchen with our distinct aroma and tickle your taste buds. Firm, plump and silver in colour which is rich in Omega 3. Make the best Rava fish fry.

items.name: Pomfret
items.description: Meet the king of the Mustard fish. Pan fry or grill it! It sure packs a punch. It has a single central bone and its fillets are perfect for those grilled steaks. Pomfret is dripping with moist, firm and tender flavours that is sure to tingle your taste buds. Leave the cleaning and cutting to our master cutters.

items.name: Anchovies / Metalu
items.description: Small fish and the big bite. This versatile fish is an ocean fish that has distinct salt and briny taste which is savory, succulent and perfect for any dish be it pizza or just a fry.The notion of good things coming in small packages rings loud with anchovies. Hiding in the fish's tiny silver glory are vitamins A, B-6, B-12, C, E, and K, omega-3 fatty acids, calcium, potassium, magnesium, phosphorus, iron, and niacin, to name a few. They're one of the most sustainable fish out there, resilient to fishing pressures with a quick reproductive cycle.

items.name: Tilapi
items.description: Let's cook the spicy chapala curry or pulusu with tamarind or bengali style tilapia aloo Maas Jhol as this is fish with mild flavour which can take flavours of the style it is being cooked. It has its home in the brackish water which gives it tender and unique mild flavour. Cook it up in a while. we will clean and cut it the way you love it.

items.name: Surmai
items.description: Meet the boss. King of the steaks with a single central bone with skin intact. High in all the goodies and yet flavourful and robust on your palate. It is perfect to grill and have with pastas. Cut into equal fillets by our master cutters so that all your fillets are cooked to perfection. Lets reel the perfect one from the ocean.

items.description: Say Hello to super food. Get excited as this is loaded with more goodness of Omega-3âs and it appeals to any palate due to its mild flavour and sumptuous texture.

items.name: Bommidala
items.description: Popular local fish from our coast which is mild yet flavourful, packs a punch when added with spices and cooked. Bommidala pulusu/stew is spicy, tangy and aromatic which activates your tastebuds and sets it on fire. It is taste and goodness combined.

items.name: Country Chicken with Skin
items.description: The all natural and freely grown chicken from the pastures of Telangana. The birds are grown in natural free farm environment and have normal feeds of grains and other things normally found in the farms. They are high in nutrition and lean meat and is perfect for those who are conscious of taste and health. We recommend cooking it in pressure cooker as it has more natural bite to it and needs little extra cooking for all the juices to be absorbed to give you the rich and unique taste of the country chicken. Curated and cut by our master butchers to give you the best. Cook your favourite Natu kodi Pulusu or the natu kodi dum biryani.
